{"tid":128992,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"MacBook Pro 入水 求救","createTime":"2017-02-21T09:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T03:52:47.000Z","uid":86604,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d7dc45864a217b8197f96338a06661c65b466a","tid":128992,"uid":86604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說剛剛係canteen，小弟嘅朋友吾小心倒瀉杯可樂入我部MacBook到。係mac機嘅出風散熱位，由機背入嘅。已經馬上拿開部機即時清理。<br />\n倒瀉嘅時候，已經即時自動關機，自己認為應該唔係好嚴重。小弟冇嘗試開機，因為怕燒。但係清理極都間唔中仲有少少可樂唔知邊度走出黎。<br />\n<br />\n有買保養，但係apple 入水好似話唔包？咁我係咪應該幫MacBook 吸左濕先 睇開唔開到機 再搵apple整？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b184bbd02d91dad7b5d42b39017ea284fa7d32","tid":128992,"uid":54546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"e820444af4a159b54b8c4afbefd7f11d47f6d4e8","tid":128992,"uid":84518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"你個friend係咪唔抵得特登速歪你部macbook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd543a473df1dc99468626f250d6d9334e84642d","tid":128992,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:12:53.000Z","msg":"吾吾吾吾你老母乎？"},{"pid":"835393880fdc5012ff125a8e3720bcd596251c88","tid":128992,"uid":6386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾你老母</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3396f5468332975580276473c7e7e81bb0d9ad7c","tid":128992,"uid":86604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個friend係咪唔抵得特登速歪你部macbook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔會咁仆街嘅，佢都話如果真係壞咗就入佢數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 